Class ProductionEffect

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.ps19.model.effect.Effect
      • it.polimi.ingsw.ps19.model.effect.ProductionEffect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Disapplyable, java.io.Serializable

    public class ProductionEffect
extends Effect
implements Disapplyable
    This class represents the production effect of a building card, it differs from other effects because its actual effect is applied only when a production on the card is activated.
